{"id":497,"date":"2017-03-10T20:25:56","date_gmt":"2017-03-10T20:25:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=497"},"modified":"2025-02-11T10:35:57","modified_gmt":"2025-02-11T10:35:57","slug":"pdf-customization","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/pdf-customization\/","title":{"rendered":"PDF Customization"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">File Location<\/h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert-info \"><strong>This is a general example how to modify the invoice PDF file<\/strong>, check on the bottom of this article for other PDF documents file locations.<\/p>\n<p>Keep in mind that you will need more developer knowledge if you are looking to make big changes to the PDF design, if you don&#8217;t, you should consider hiring a developer to do this for you.<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>The invoice PDF template is located in <strong>application\/views\/themes\/perfex\/views\/invoicepdf.php<\/strong>. With Perfex you have the ability to edit all the files located on application\/views without editing the core files so in this case you won&#8217;t need to worry about the updates except if any huge changes are made in the files, check the link below for more information, in this case, your filename should be <strong>my_invoicepdf.php<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-perfex-crm wp-block-embed-perfex-crm\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"AGSJOuCgdG\"><a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/edit-view-files-without-messing-the-core-view-files\/\">Edit view files without messing the core view files<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden;\" title=\"&#8220;Edit view files without messing the core view files&#8221; &#8212; Perfex CRM\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/edit-view-files-without-messing-the-core-view-files\/embed\/#?secret=rTE9Z9jWRI#?secret=AGSJOuCgdG\" data-secret=\"AGSJOuCgdG\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Editing the Text and the Content of the&nbsp;PDF document.<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>You can customize the PDF Invoices and add or remove some text changing your layout or images. Perfex CRM uses <strong>the TCPDF library for generating PDF documents<\/strong>. Here is the direct link to all functions available in the TCPDF library:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/tcpdf.org\/docs\/srcdoc\/TCPDF\/class-TCPDF\/\">https:\/\/tcpdf.org\/docs\/srcdoc\/tcpdf\/class-TCPDF\/<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additional examples can be found at the following link:<a href=\"https:\/\/tcpdf.org\/examples\/\">\u00a0https:\/\/tcpdf.org\/examples\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using this TCPDF Library you can edit the PDF templates. Note that you will need PHP knowledge to modify the file.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Adding a Custom PDF Logo<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>Probably you will have problems with PNG images with transparency that are handled in a different way depending on the php-imagick or php-gd version used. Try to update php-imagick and disable php-gd, if you leave this field blank the <strong>uploaded company logo will be used.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Go to\u00a0<strong>Setup->Settings->PDF ->\u00a0Custom PDF Company Logo URL<\/strong>. You can adjust your\u00a0logo width also see the picture below.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"109\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/PDF-Logo-768x279-300x109.png\" alt=\"pdf customization\" class=\"wp-image-509\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/PDF-Logo-768x279-300x109.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/PDF-Logo-768x279.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/PDF-Logo-768x279-60x22.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/PDF-Logo-768x279-150x54.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>If can&#8217;t see the logo, you can apply a workaround as explained here: <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/tcpdf-error-image-unable-to-get-the-size-of-the-image\/\">https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/tcpdf-error-image-unable-to-get-the-size-of-the-image\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Items Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you need to customize the items tables (HTML and PDF), the best is to take a look in application\/libraries\/<strong>App_items_table.php<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">PDF Document Formats<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can find all PDF document formats in <strong>Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;PDF-&gt;Document Formats.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"998\" height=\"760\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-document-formats.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-document-formats.png 998w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-document-formats-300x228.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-document-formats-768x585.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-document-formats-60x46.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-document-formats-150x114.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong><div class=\"st-alert st-alert- \">Note that when you customize the PDF and you remove the ability to apply these options you won&#8217;t be able to see any changes while applying options from the settings area.<\/div><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can always adjust one template that fit for your needs based on your colors, font sizes etc.. and use it for your own requirements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">PDF Font Family<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When you first purchase Perfex CRM the PDF font <strong>freesans<\/strong> will be used.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This font is the default because of supports UTF-8. PDF files may be larger using this font if your company does not need UTF-8 support and your customers are not using any special characters in their data or in the language you are using you can change to font to Eq. Helvetica or try changing the font until it best fits your requirements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>For <strong>Arabic <\/strong>characters use font: <strong>dejavusans <\/strong>or <strong>aealarabiya<\/strong> or <strong>aefurat<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>For <strong>Japanese <\/strong>and <strong>Chinese <\/strong>use font: <strong>droidsansfallback<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>For Cyrillic characters use font: <strong>freesans<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Changing the font is available from the settings at <strong>Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;PDF<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"change_heading\">Changing Invoice\/Estimate PDF Heading<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you need to change the heading on the right side (see images below for more info) for estimates and invoices you can overwrite the translation text by creating custom_lang.php, read more <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/overwrite-translation-text\/\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Change Heading to Invoices<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"50\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-3-300x50.png\" alt=\"pdf customization\" class=\"wp-image-500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-3-300x50.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-3-768x127.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-3-60x10.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-3-150x25.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-3.png 769w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Language key:<strong>&nbsp;$lang[&#8216;invoice_pdf_heading&#8217;] = &#8216;Invoice&#8217;;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Change heading to Estimates<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"45\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-4-300x45.png\" alt=\"pdf customization\" class=\"wp-image-501\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-4-300x45.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-4-768x116.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-4-60x9.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-4-150x23.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/pdf-logo-4.png 770w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Language key:<strong> $lang[&#8216;estimate_pdf_heading&#8217;] = &#8216;Estimate&#8217;;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Additional options.<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, you can find more options in\u00a0<strong>Setup->Settings->PDF<\/strong>. Check the pictures below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"996\" height=\"742\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Vo4G6Le.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4377\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Vo4G6Le.png 996w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Vo4G6Le-300x223.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Vo4G6Le-768x572.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Vo4G6Le-60x45.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/Vo4G6Le-150x112.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 996px) 100vw, 996px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"mw-headline\">Troubleshooting<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-perfex-crm wp-block-embed-perfex-crm\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"Dnm2CF2nqO\"><a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/tcpdf-error-image-unable-to-get-the-size-of-the-image\/\">TCPDF ERROR: [Image] Unable to Get the Size of the Image<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden;\" title=\"&#8220;TCPDF ERROR: [Image] Unable to Get the Size of the Image&#8221; &#8212; Perfex CRM\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/tcpdf-error-image-unable-to-get-the-size-of-the-image\/embed\/#?secret=MKaTlfg2qm#?secret=Dnm2CF2nqO\" data-secret=\"Dnm2CF2nqO\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">PDF Language<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>If customer language is System Default the default language that is selected in <strong>Setup->Settings->Localization<\/strong> will be used on PDF documents.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>When you are in the admin area and system\/staff language is e.q English and customer default language is Spanish the invoice will be still downloaded in English, if you want when you are in the admin area, to download the PDF documents in customers language, check <strong>Setup->Settings->Localization <\/strong>the option <strong>Output client PDF documents from admin area in client language<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>When the customer views<\/strong> the invoice or downloads the invoice PDF from customer&#8217;s invoice preview area, he\/she will be able to see the invoice in his <strong>default language that is set in the customer profile<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Other PDF Templates<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>If u want to edit <strong>other pdf templates<\/strong>&nbsp;you can achieve this by editing the files, the process is the same like invoices.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong><g class=\"gr_ gr_35 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar only-ins doubleReplace replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"35\" data-gr-id=\"35\">Estimate<\/g> PDF <\/strong>location:  application\/views\/themes\/perfex\/views\/<strong>estimatepdf.php<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><g class=\"gr_ gr_36 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar only-ins doubleReplace replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"36\" data-gr-id=\"36\">Proposal<\/g><\/strong>\u00a0<strong>PDF<\/strong> location: application\/views\/themes\/perfex\/views\/<strong>proposalpdf.php<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Payment Receipt<\/strong> location: application\/views\/themes\/perfex\/views\/<strong>paymentpdf.php<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Contract PDF  <\/strong>location: application\/views\/themes\/perfex\/views\/<strong>contractpdf.php.<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><g class=\"gr_ gr_77 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar only-ins doubleReplace replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"77\" data-gr-id=\"77\">Statement<\/g> PDF<\/strong> location:  application\/views\/themes\/perfex\/views\/statementpdf.php (v1.8.0 required)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Credit Note PDF<\/strong> location: application\/views\/themes\/perfex\/views\/credit_note_pdf.php<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out <a href=\"https:\/\/fixthephoto.com\/top-pdf-organizers.html\" title=\"PDF Organizers\">PDF organizers<\/a> to use for managing, rotating, deleting, inserting, substituting, and rearranging the pages in your PDFs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>File Location The invoice PDF template is located in application\/views\/themes\/perfex\/views\/invoicepdf.php. With Perfex you have the ability to edit all the files located on application\/views without editing the core files so in this case you won&#8217;t need to worry about the updates except if any huge changes are made in the files, check the link below [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[22],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-497","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-customization"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/497","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{